\/","url_meta":{"origin":23214,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Injustice: Supplication of oppressed always answered","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aslam reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, appointed a client of his named Hunayy to tend the pasture, saying, \u201cO Hunayy, lower your wing for the Muslims and beware the supplication of the oppressed, for the supplication of the oppressed is answered.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3059\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32236,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/17\/travelers-parents-oppressed\/","url_meta":{"origin":23214,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Travelers, parents, oppressed answered by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe supplications of three people are answered: the traveler, the parents, and the oppressed.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 17399 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064f\u0647\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width"